Package com.uco.ucodgt.mvc.model.business.user.client

Class ClientDTO

java.lang.Object
com.uco.ucodgt.mvc.model.business.user.client.ClientDTO
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ClientDTO extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a client user in the system. This class encapsulates the data associated with a client user, including their unique identification number (DNI), password, name, surname, age, email address, date of obtaining the driver's license, date of last update, and accumulated license points.
